Supporting the exchange of best practices in the area of smart automation;
Transfer of know-how and support of employees in the application of smart automation solutions at ZF;
Collaborate with cross-functional teams to ensure seamless integration of automation technologies;
Develop and maintain automation standards and best practices for the organization together with Product Line heads;
Research and evaluate new technologies and recommend solutions to enhance automation capabilities;
